.TH "SVGAELEMENT.PATHNAME" "3JS" "October 21, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SVGAElement.pathname \- SVGAElement: pathname property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]pathname\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string containing an initial \f[CR]/\f[R] followed
by the path of the URL, not including the query string or fragment.
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs pathname.
.SH VALUE
A string.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IP \(bu 2
SVG \f[CR]<a>\f[R] element
